# App Versioning

- This app must always have a visible version number based on `package.json`.
- Any code change, UI change, bug fix, behavior change, or dependency change must include a version bump.
- Keep `package.json` and `package-lock.json` version values in sync.
- Default bump policy:
  - Patch: small fixes or small UI/wording changes
  - Minor: new features or meaningful behavior additions
  - Major: breaking or compatibility-affecting changes
- When editing this project, update the version first or as part of the same change.
- Do not leave code changes unversioned.
